The paper discusses various information access tasks related to web tables, such as table extraction, interpretation, search, question answering, knowledge base augmentation, and table augmentation. These tasks are closely related to several subfields of computer science, including information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
